Librero></button><button class="draw desktop1" title=Escritorio></button></div><div class=section><h1>Dormitorio</h1><button class="draw bed1" title="Cama Simple"></button><button class="draw bed2" title="Cama Doble"></button><button class="draw stand1" title="Mesa de Noche"></button></div><div class=section><h1>Baño</h1><button class="draw sink1" title="Lavamanos Rectangular"></button><button class="draw sink2" title="Lavamanos Circular"></button><button class="draw toilet1" title=Retrete></button><button class="draw bathtub1" title="Tina Rectangular"></button><button class="draw bathtub2" title="Tina Ovalada"></button><button class="draw bathtub3" title="Tina Redondeada"></button><button class="draw shower1" title="Ducha simple"></button><button class="draw shower2" title="Ducha redonda"></button><button class="draw shower3" title="Ducha esquinada"></button></div><div class=section><h1>Cocina</h1><button class="draw basin1" title="Lavaplatos Simple"></button><button class="draw basin2" title="Lavaplatos Doble"></button><button class="draw cooker1" title="Estufa de 4 Hornillas"></button><button class="draw cooker2" title="Estufa de 2 Hornillas"></button><button class="draw fridge1" title="Refrigerador Ovalado"></button><button class="draw fridge2" title="Refrigerador Rectangular"></button><button class="draw counter1" title=Mesón></button></div><div class=section><h1>Instalaciones</h1><button class="draw meter" title="Medidor de Gas"></button><button class="draw piston1" title="Cocina-Horno Horizontal"></button><button class="draw piston2" title="Cocina-Horno Vertical"></button><button class="draw input" title="Entrada de aire"></button><button class="draw output" title="Salida de gases de combustión"></button><button class="draw aeration" title="Aireación Rapida"></button><button class="draw heater" title="Previsto calefón"></button><button class="draw gasline1" title="Tuberia de Gas"></button><button class="draw gasline2" title="Tuberia de Gas enterrada"></button